      "rationale": "Components are copied directly into the user project rather than installed as a dependency so users own the code and can modify it freely. Zero runtime dependencies \u2014 each component is a standalone .tsx file. CSS variables are used instead of hardcoded colors so components follow any Tailwind theme in light and dark mode without extra config."
